cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY 

This paper deals with improving the learning speed and performance of neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the use of second-order optimization methods, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the experiments involve image classification, which is a common application of computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the analysis of connections to second-order optimization methods suggests a potential application in control systems (cs.SY).
